    "He is chairman, managing director and chief cardiac surgeon at Medanta, which offers services across more than 30 specialties including cardiology, neurology and oncology.",
    "Medanta has six hospitals across North India with more than 3,500 hospital beds",
    "He listed Global Health, the parent company of Medanta, on the Indian bourses in 2022."
  ],
  "about": [
